Clint's '''Blacksmith''' shop provides multiple services primarily related to [[:Category:Resources|resources]] found in [[the Mines]]. It chiefly serves as a location for upgrading [[tools]], and breaking open [[Minerals#Geodes|geodes]], although he also trades in [[Coal]] and ores ([[Copper Ore|copper]], [[Iron Ore|iron]], &amp; [[Gold Ore|gold]]). Finally, the building is also [[Clint]]'s home, and his bedroom is out the back of the shop floor.

==Stock==
The purchase prices of ore and coal increase in Years 2+. The player will receive a letter in the mail on [[Spring]] 1 of Year 2 saying "Notice: The price of raw materials at [[Carpenter's Shop|Robin's shop]] and Clint's shop has increased." The gold obtained by selling items to Clint (or through the [[Shipping|shipping bin]]) does not increase.
